channel.title: StringWrapper is gone
channel.description:
Jagex has removed their class to hold String values... As far as I can tell it has been replaced in #532 by String everywhere... At least that seems to be the most logical explanation...
And here's the proof: [code] ^ bd implements com.freddy.hooks.Player * getName() --> java.lang.String bd.tc * getLevel() --> int bd.yc[/code] I'm certain that these hooks are correct.
